================================================================================
ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR MEDIA DOWNLOADING TOOL
================================================================================

This software is a TOOL that enables users to download media content from
various online platforms. The software itself does not host, store, or 
distribute any copyrighted content.

USERS ARE SOLELY RESPONSIBLE FOR:
- Ensuring compliance with applicable copyright laws
- Respecting platform Terms of Service
- Obtaining necessary permissions for content download
- Any legal consequences arising from their use of this software

LEGITIMATE USE CASES INCLUDE:
- Backing up your own uploaded content
- Downloading Creative Commons licensed content
- Educational use under Fair Use doctrine
- Archiving public domain materials
- Personal backup of legally purchased content

PROHIBITED USES:
- Downloading copyrighted content without permission
- Commercial redistribution of downloaded content
- Violating platform Terms of Service
- Mass downloading for commercial purposes
- Any illegal activities

THE DEVELOPERS OF THIS SOFTWARE:
- Do not encourage or condone copyright infringement
- Assume no liability for user actions
- Provide this tool for legitimate archival and backup purposes only
- Reserve the right to refuse support for any illegal use

By using this software, you acknowledge that you understand these terms
and agree to use the software only for legitimate, legal purposes.

If you believe this tool is being misused or have legal concerns, please
contact the repository maintainer.
